{"tid":2075154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"初選民調-新西   黃子悅 vs 朱凱廸","createTime":"2020-06-22T15:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:11:29.000Z","uid":1249,"like":61,"dislike":181,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc09054a63f0621b3dbae20f1de0ed40d263fab","tid":2075154,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"黃子悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朱Heidi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d8de8de2773e78f6f4737c77b93f265f48337c","tid":2075154,"uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"黃子悅（英語：Prince Wong Ji-yuet，1997年9月27日－），前學民思潮前發言人，曾於2014年雨傘革命時，絕食118個小時而聞名。2015年5月開始擔任學民思潮發言人[1]，學民思潮解散後成為教育實驗學社成員[2]。現於香港嶺南大學就讀視覺研究，2017-18學年曾經因為精神健康問題休學一年[3]。2020年5月接受媒體訪問，表示考慮參與2020年立法會新界西議席選舉[4]。<br />\n<br />\n聲援理大行動<br />\n2019年11月18日，大批市民為營救被警方圍困的理工大學學生，湧至油尖旺多個街頭與警方爆發激烈衝突，在衝突中，警方拘捕逾千名市民，黃子悅是其中一名被捕人士。黃子悅被控暴動罪，後獲准保釋候審，期間須要遵守宵禁令、包括油麻地至旺角一帶的禁足令、不得離開香港及每周到警署報到[5]。"},{"pid":"481042d15c565df841160eb686f7febecda81261","tid":2075154,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"黃子悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf29b6c21c9e6aab4f0cf29b07be5b17dded6b0","tid":2075154,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"朱凱廸（英語：Eddie Chu Hoi-dick，1977年9月29日－），香港立法會議員（新界西），社會運動活躍人士、左翼環境保護主義者，是土地正義聯盟成員，加入民主派立法會黨團議會陣線運作。在反對清拆皇后碼頭行動中，朱凱廸曾是本土行動的成員，代表該組織向大眾介紹文物保育、城市規劃民主化的重要性而為人熟悉[5]，並且長期關注新界的鄉郊發展。他也是菜園村關注組成員，是反高鐵運動的中堅人物[6]。<br />\n<br />\n2019年佔領立法會事件<br />\n2019年7月1日，部分反對逃犯條例修訂的激進示威者衝入立法會大樓內，當時隨示威者入內的朱凱迪分別以中、英語向記者指出示威人士並不是追求普選權（「People here are not even demanding universal suffrage」）。有關言論隨即被在場人士反駁，也受到網民大加鞭伐。[51][52]"},{"pid":"a14aabddb5785b39f8a5d3ade3c6cad602f56d1f","tid":2075154,"uid":63069,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"both得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Heidi都叫做有進步嘅"},{"pid":"c7ea73f403684fd6905fcc409e0a098ece873a74","tid":2075154,"uid":142002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"一定係投Heidi對抗鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758744294436042563426ff42d40d3c12fc7fb28","tid":2075154,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"黃子悅ig啲相幾靚<br />\n但google返佢以前差咁撚遠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0ed6b622e7c10a8e1ae4f1ee7fc2316900a48d","tid":2075154,"uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNrp9jF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNrp9jF.png&h=99a2ec20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200210/_2020021018095872026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200210%2F_2020021018095872026.jpg&h=5430cb2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19b980e72759eb5cd031615016fc16d13dfff1e4","tid":2075154,"uid":39010,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"雖然算靚 但SORRY<br />\n都係朱凱廸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173e43fd46a37f540bb84e71612f5f676d770683","tid":2075154,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"做咩咁多POST 2揀一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434c8e9c62d31eab40ec85b5e415bbb1c5239fb0","tid":2075154,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173e43fd46a37f540bb84e71612f5f676d770683","tid":2075154,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0